We have to stop meeting like this ...

}    if [[ -n $@ ]] ; then
}       listalloptions | egrep "${@:s/ /|/}"
}    else listalloptions
}    fi;

That doesn't work, does it?

    zsh% argv=(x y z)
    zsh% print -l "${@:s/ /|/}"
    x
    y
    z
    zsh% print -l "${(j:|:)@}"
    x|y|z
    zsh% print -l "${*:gs/ /|/}"
    x|y|z

